            <div style="background: #d1ecf1; border: 1px solid #0c5460; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">⚠️ Content Moved</h4>
                <p>The Todo System Update Plan has been reorganized as a <strong>sub-project</strong> under the <strong>Planning System</strong> group.</p>
